      <abstract id="aspace_af945b4b409dcaeb3b249d7fba5bffdb">Journal of an unidentified slave
        overseer listing slave names and amount of crops each picked. Also lists when and which
        slaves were sick each day, money obtained for a crop, home remedies for common illnesses,
        and the journey itinerary for a cargo ship.</abstract>
